    "description": "BikeDekho Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Digital Marketing Manager for our Jabalpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout BikeDekho Advisory Limited:\nBikeDekho Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BikeDekho Advisory Limited!",
